174:| **Amazon S3** | Stores versioned patient feature vectors and outcome datasets |
175:| **AWS Glue** | Runs nightly ETL to transform raw EHR/claims data into engineered features |
176:| **Amazon DynamoDB** | Caches similarity results to avoid redundant inference; TTL-based expiration |
